3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg1vqy4py0o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg1vqy4py0o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20minister%20Resigns%20After%20Close%20Aide%20Arrested%20Over%20Murder%20Of%20Sarpanch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20minister%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20has%20resigned%20after%20one%20of%20his%20close%20aides%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20chilling%20murder%20of%20a%20sarpanch%20in%20Beed%20district%20in%20December.%20Mr%20Munde%2C%20who%20held%20the%20portfolios%20of%20food%20and%20civil%20supplies%2C%20has%20stepped%20down%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20after%20his%20aide%20Walmik%20Karad%20was%20arrested%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%2C%20the%20sarpanch%20of%20Massajog%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Munde%20said%20it%20has%20been%20his%20firm%20demand%20that%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20sarpanch's%20murder%20case%20get%20the%20harshest%20punishment.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20the%20photos%20that%20surfaced%20yesterday%2C%20I%20was%20deeply%20saddened.%20The%20investigation%20into%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20completed%20and%20the%20charge%20sheet%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20court.%20Also%2C%20a%20judicial%20inquiry%20is%20proposed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0The%20NCP%20leader%20said%20he%20had%20heard%20his%20%26quot%3Binner%20self%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20the%20decision.%20He%20said%20his%20health%20has%20also%20not%20been%20well%20and%20the%20doctor%20had%20advised%20him%20to%20undergo%20treatment%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20had%20accepted%20Mr%20Munde's%20resignation%20and%20had%20forwarded%20it%20to%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20missive%20from%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20came%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20discuss%20the%20political%20fallout%20of%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20sarpanch's%20murder%20case%20and%20what%20the%20investigation%20revealed%20about%20Karad's%20alleged%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-nine-year-old%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20and%20represents%20Beed's%20Parli%20seat%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20nephew%20of%20BJP%20veteran%2C%20the%20late%20Gopinath%20Munde%2C%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20is%20a%20cousin%20of%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Pankaja%20Munde.%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20joined%20the%20NCP%20in%202013.%20When%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20party%20split%20in%202023%2C%20he%20sided%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20he%20has%20served%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20legislative%20council%20and%20as%20a%20state%20minister%20in%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBehind%20Minister's%20Ouster%2C%20A%20Chilling%20Murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantosh%20Deshmukh%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20sarpanch%20of%20Massajog%20village%20in%20Beed%2C%20was%20abducted%2C%20tortured%20and%20murdered%20on%20December%209%20after%20he%20tried%20to%20stop%20an%20extortion%20attempt%20targeting%20an%20energy%20company%2C%20the%20investigation%20has%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%20of%20state%20police%20filed%20a%201%2C200-page%20chargesheet%20in%20a%20district%20court%20on%20February%2027.%20Three%20cases%20--%20relating%20to%20the%20sarpanch's%20murder%2C%20attempt%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20Avaada%20company%20and%20an%20assault%20on%20security%20guard%20of%20the%20firm%20--%20have%20been%20registered.%20The%20stringent%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%20has%20been%20invoked%20against%20eight%20accused.%20Seven%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20one%20is%20on%20the%20run.%20Among%20the%20arrested%20accused%20is%20Karad%2C%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Dhananjay%20Munde%2C%20building%20pressure%20on%20the%20state%20government%20to%20act%20against%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrutal%20Torture%2C%20Shocking%20Videos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnatosh%20Deshmukh%20was%20abducted%20by%20six%20men%20in%20an%20SUV%20on%20December%209%20at%20Dongaon%20toll%20plaza%20and%20taken%20towards%20Kej%20taluka.%20He%20was%20found%20unconscious%20at%20Daithna%20Shivar%20towards%20Nandur%20Ghat%20Road%20that%20evening.%20He%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20officials%2C%20he%20was%20beaten%20between%20for%20over%20two%20hours%20with%20a%20gas%20pipe%20an%20iron%20rod%2C%20wooden%20sticks%20and%20sharp%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20that%20Santosh%20Deshmukh%20was%20tortured%20before%20being%20killed%20and%20the%20assailants%20recorded%2015%20videos%2C%20clicked%20eight%20photos%20and%20even%20made%20two%20video%20calls%20to%20document%20the%20brutality.%C2%A0In%20one%20of%20the%20videos%20mentioned%20in%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20five%20accused%20are%20seen%20thrashing%20Mr%20Deshmukh%20with%20a%20white%20pipe%20and%20a%20wooden%20stick%2C%20and%20kicking%20and%20punching%20him.%20The%20video%20shows%20Deshmukh%20in%20a%20half-naked%20condition.%C2%A0Another%20video%20shows%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20urinating%20on%20him%20as%20he%20bleeds%20heavily%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741068420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Flgdfi2t_dhananjay-munde-_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-minister-dhananjay-munde-resigns-after-close-aide-arrested-over-murder-of-sarpanch-7843219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20minister%20Dhananjay%20Munde%20Resigns%20After%20Close%20Aide%20A