move%20came%20as%20America%20doubled%20duties%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20to%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20along%20with%20imposing%20new%2025%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20launching%20new%20trade%20conflicts%20with%20the%20top%20three%20US%20trading%20partners%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeijing%20will%20impose%20an%20additional%2015%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20US%20chicken%2C%20wheat%2C%20corn%20and%20cotton%20and%20an%20extra%2010%20per%20cent%20levy%20on%20US%20soybeans%2C%20sorghum%2C%20pork%2C%20beef%2C%20aquatic%20products%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20and%20dairy%20imports%20from%20March%2010%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20finance%20ministry%20announced%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20China's%20commerce%20ministry%20said%20the%20unilateral%20tariff%20measures%20of%20the%20United%20States%20seriously%20violate%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20rules%20and%20undermine%20the%20basis%20for%20economic%20and%20trade%20cooperation%20between%20China%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20will%20firmly%20safeguard%20its%20legitimate%20rights%20and%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Tariffs%20On%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extra%2010%20per%20cent%20duty%2C%20which%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20China%20with%20last%20week%2C%20entered%20into%20force%20at%200501%20GMT%20on%20March%204%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20cumulative%2020%20per%20cent%20tariff%20in%20response%20to%20what%20the%20White%20House%20considers%20Chinese%20inaction%20over%20drug%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cumulative%2020%20per%20cent%20duty%20also%20comes%20on%20top%20of%20tariffs%20of%20up%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20imposed%20by%20Trump%20during%20his%20first%20term%20on%20some%20%24370%20billion%20worth%20of%20US%20imports.%20Some%20of%20these%20products%20saw%20American%20tariffs%20increase%20sharply%20under%20former%20president%20Joe%20Biden%20last%20year%2C%20including%20a%20doubling%20of%20duties%20on%20Chinese%20semiconductors%20to%2050%20per%20cent%20and%20a%20quadrupling%20of%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20over%20100%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020%20per%20cent%20tariff%20will%20apply%20to%20several%20major%20US%20consumer%20electronics%20imports%20from%20China%20previously%20untouched%20by%20prior%20duties%2C%20including%20smartphones%2C%20laptops%2C%20videogame%20consoles%2C%20smartwatches%2C%20speakers%20and%20Bluetooth%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20argued%20that%20China%20supplies%20chemicals%20used%20in%20fentanyl%20production.%20China%20has%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741067820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-11%2Ftrump-xi-650-reuters_650x400_81510231282.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-retaliates-announces-15-tariff-on-import-of-these-items-from-us-7843287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20swiftly%20retaliated%20against%20fresh%20US%20tariffs%20announced%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20and%20announced%2010%20to%2015%20per%20cent%20hikes%20to%20import%20levies%20covering%20a%20range%20of%20American%20agricultural%20and%20food%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-retaliates-announces-15-tariff-on-import-of-these-items-from-us-7843287%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Family%20Of%20Indian%20Student%20In%20Coma%20Reaches%20US%2C%20Shares%20Health%20Update%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nilam-shinde-indian-student-critical-after-accident-in-us-7813735%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENilam%20Shinde%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20woman%20wh