0Sharma%20and%20former%20captain%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20said%20the%20latter%20always%20compliments%20other%20cricketers.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20spoke%20in%20a%20generic%20manner.%20I%20fail%20to%20understand%20how%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20the%20right%20to%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20drew%20a%20wave%20of%20criticism%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20responded%20by%20questioning%20the%20Opposition%20party's%20criticism.%20%26quot%3BShame%20on%20Congress!%20Now%20they%20are%20going%20after%20the%20Indian%20Cricket%20Captain!%20Do%20they%20expect%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20now%20play%20cricket%20after%20failing%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20board%20termed%20the%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B.%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Devajit%20Saikia%20said%20such%20comments%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20ICC%20event%20could%20have%20a%20demoralising%20effect%20on%20a%20cricketer's%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20unfortunate%20for%20a%20responsible%20person%20to%20pass%20such%20a%20trivial%20comment%20when%20the%20team%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20such%20a%20crucial%20ICC%20tournament.%20It%20may%20have%20demoralising%20effect%20on%20an%20individual%20or%20the%20team.%20All%20the%20players%20are%20performing%20to%20their%20highest%20potential%20and%20results%20are%20visible.%20I%20hope%20individuals%20will%20desist%20from%20making%20such%20derogatory%20statements%20for%20personal%20publicity%20sake%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Devajit%20Saikia%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20they%20did%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20position.%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20party's%20publicity%20department%2C%20said%20she%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20delete%20the%20social%20media%20posts.%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Shama%20Mohammed%2C%20National%20Spokesperson%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20made%20certain%20remarks%20about%20a%20cricketing%20legend%20that%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20position.%20She%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20delete%20the%20concerned%20social%20media%20posts%20from%20X%20and%20has%20been%20advised%20to%20exercise%20greater%20caution%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20holds%20the%20contributions%20of%20sporting%20icons%20in%20the%20highest%20regard%20and%20does%20not%20endorse%20any%20statements%20that%20undermine%20their%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khera%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mohamed's%20remarks%2C%20however%2C%20found%20endorsement%20from%20an%20unlikely%20quarter.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Sougata%20Ray%20said%20she%20had%20not%20said%20anything%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20Mr%20Ray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20performance%20has%20been%20quite%20poor.%20He%20scored%20one%20century%2C%20but%20other%20than%20that%2C%20he%20gets%20out%20after%20scoring%202%2C%203%2C%204%2C%20or%205%20runs.%20He%20shouldn't%20be%20(on%20the%20team).%20India%20wins%20because%20the%20other%20players%20play%20well%2C%20but%20the%20captain%20doesn't%20contribute.%26quot%3B%20The%20veteran%20leader%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Shama%20Mohamed%20has%20said%20is%20correct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-seven-year-old%20Rohit%20Sharma%20took%20over%20as%20Team%20India%20captain%20in%202023.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20India%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20and%20two%20Asia%20Cup%20trophies%20earlier.%20He%20has%20a%20stellar%20record%20in%20IPL%20too.%20As%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%2C%20he%20has%20led%20the%20team%20to%20five%20IPL%20titles.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20set%20for%20the%20big%20match%20as%20India%20takes%20on%20Australia%20in%20the%20fir