%3Bthere%20is%20no%20justification%26quot%3B%20for%20Washington's%20actions%20and%20vowed%20to%20slap%20tariffs%20on%20US%20imports%20beginning%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20the%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%2C%20Americans%20will%20pay%20more%20for%20groceries%2C%20gas%20and%20cars%2C%20and%20potentially%20lose%20thousands%20of%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20will%20disrupt%20an%20incredibly%20successful%20trading%20relationship.%20They%20will%20violate%20the%20very%20trade%20agreement%20that%20was%20negotiated%20by%20President%20Trump%20in%20his%20last%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20said%20his%20country%20will%20retaliate%20by%20putting%2025%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20American%20goods%20worth%20%24155%20billion%20Canadian%20over%20the%20course%20of%2021%20days%2C%20starting%20with%20taxes%20on%20goods%20worth%20%2430%20billion%20Canadian%20after%20midnight%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20Vows%20Countermeasures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20commerce%20ministry%20on%20Tuesday%20voiced%20opposition%20against%20a%20U.S.%20decision%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20products%20related%20to%20fentanyl%20and%20other%20issues%2C%20vowing%20countermeasures%20that%20it%20said%20were%20aimed%20at%20safeguarding%20its%20rights%20and%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20%26quot%3Bshifted%20the%20blame%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20using%20its%20problems%20with%20deadly%20drug%20fentanyl%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20impose%20tariffs%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20argued%20that%20China%20supplies%20chemicals%20used%20in%20fentanyl%20production.%20China%20has%20denied%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20urges%20the%20US%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20withdraw%26quot%3B%20its%20unilateral%20tariff%20measures%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bunreasonable%20and%20groundless%2C%20harmful%20to%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMexico%20Promises%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexico's%20economy%20ministry%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20public%20response%20until%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum's%20regular%20morning%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%20After%20avoiding%20the%20first%20round%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs%20by%20striking%20a%20last-minute%20deal%20to%20send%20thousands%20of%20troops%20to%20its%20northern%20border%2C%20Mexico%20has%20stepped%20up%20anti-drug%20efforts%20and%20hinted%20at%20new%20measures%20on%20imported%20Chinese%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20President%20Sheinbaum%20went%20into%20waiting%20to%20see%20what%20Trump%20would%20say.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20decision%20that%20depends%20on%20the%20United%20States%20government%2C%20on%20the%20United%20States%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheinbaum%20said%20ahead%20of%20Trump's%20statement.%20%26quot%3BSo%20whatever%20his%20decision%20is%2C%20we%20will%20make%20our%20decisions%20and%20there%20is%20a%20plan%2C%20there%20is%20unity%20in%20Mexico.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%2025%20per%20cent%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20Tuesday%2C%20sparking%20renewed%20fears%20of%20a%20North%20American%20trade%20war%20that%20already%20showed%20signs%20of%20pushing%20up%20inflation%20and%20hindering%20growth.%20He%20also%20reaffirmed%20that%20he%20will%20increase%20tariffs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20imports%20to%2020%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20previous%2010%20per%20cent%20levy%20to%20punish%20Beijing%20for%20failing%20to%20halt%20shipments%20of%20fentanyl%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20remains%20confident%20that%20tariffs%20are%20the%20best%20choice%20to%20boost%20US%20manufacturing%20and%20attract%20fo