A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwarren-buffett-on-donald-trumps-tariffs-on-canada-china-mexico-an-act-of-war-7842775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20Tariffs%20Cause%20Global%20Markets%20Meltdown%2C%20Nifty%20Opens%20In%20Red%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStock%20markets%20across%20the%20globe%20sank%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20would%20go%20into%20effect%20as%20planned.%C2%A0Trump's%20comments%20made%20on%20Monday%20struck%20fears%20of%20a%20trade%20war%20in%20North%20America%20and%20sent%20financial%20markets%20reeling.%20The%20US%20stocks%20tumbled%20sharply%20in%20late%20afternoon%20trading%2C%20while%20the%20Mexican%20peso%20and%20Canadian%20dollar%20also%20fell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20President%20has%20said%20that%2025%20percent%20American%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20Tuesday%20after%20the%2030-day%20pause%20on%20duties%2C%20tied%20to%20illegal%20border%20crossings%20and%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl%20into%20the%20United%20States%20expires.%C2%A0The%20American%20also%20reaffirmed%20that%20he%20will%20increase%20tariffs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20imports%20to%2020%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20previous%2010%20per%20cent%20levy%20to%20punish%20Beijing%20for%20failing%20to%20halt%20shipments%20of%20fentanyl%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Trump%20Said%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20have%20a%20tariff.%20So%20what%20they%20have%20to%20do%20is%20build%20their%20car%20plants%2C%20frankly%2C%20and%20other%20things%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20in%20which%20case%20they%20have%20no%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20room%20left%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20deal%20that%20would%20avert%20the%20tariffs%20by%20curbing%20fentanyl%20flows%20into%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20hiking%20tariffs%20on%20all%20Chinese%20imports%2C%20the%20president%20said%20in%20an%20order%20that%20Beijing%20%26quot%3Bhas%20not%20taken%20adequate%20steps%20to%20alleviate%20the%20illicit%20drug%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20effect%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20EST%20(0501%20GMT)%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20confirmed%20in%20Federal%20Register%20notices.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20the%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20agency%20will%20begin%20collecting%2025%20per%20cent%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20goods%2C%20with%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20duty%20for%20Canadian%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20maintained%20that%20tariffs%20were%20a%20useful%20tool%20to%20correct%20trade%20imbalances%20and%20protect%20US%20manufacturing%2C%20dismissing%20concerns%20that%20the%20measures%20risk%20economic%20damage%20in%20the%20US%2C%20despite%20the%20close%20ties%2C%20especially%20in%20North%20America%2C%20where%20businesses%20have%20enjoyed%20decades%20of%20free%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CEOs%20and%20economists%2C%20Trump's%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20covering%20more%20than%20%24900%20billion%20worth%20of%20annual%20US%20imports%2C%20will%20deal%20a%20serious%20setback%20to%20the%20highly%20integrated%20North%20American%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada%2C%20Mexico%20And%20China%20Respond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexico's%20economy%20ministry%20said%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20public%20response%20until%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum's%20regular%20morning%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%20On%20Monday%2C%20she%20appeared%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20Trump%20when%20she%20said%20at%20a%20public%20event%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Colima%20that%20%26quot%3BMexico%20has%20to%20be%20respected%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20vowed%20to%20respond%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20plan%20B%2C%20C%2C%20D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20told%20reporters%20that%20Ottawa%20was%20ready%20to%20respond%2C%20but%20offered%20no%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOntario%20Premier%20Doug%20Ford%20told%20NBC%20that%20the%20U.S.%20tariffs%20and%20Canada's%20retaliation%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ban%20absolute%20disaster%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20countries.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20respond%20but%20we%20will%20respond%20like%20they've%20never%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Ford%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Michigan%20auto%20plants%20would%20likely%20shut%20down%20within%20a%20week%20and%20that%20he%20would%20halt%20nickel%20shipments%20and%20cross-border%20transmission%20of%20electricity%20from%20Ontario%20to%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20after%20absolutely%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Ford%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China's%20state-run%20Global%20Times%20newspaper%20said%20that%20Beijing%20had%20prepared%20countermeasures%2C%20which%20would%20probably%20target%20US%20agricultural%20and%20food%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarkets%20Swoons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20major%20indexes%20in%20the%20US%20sank%20after%20Trump's%20comments.%20The%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20ended%20the%20day%20down%20649.67%20points%2C%20or%201.48%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20lost%20104.78%20points%2C%20or%201.76%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20dropped%20497.09%20points%2C%20or%202.64%20per%20cent.%20A%20gauge%20of%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20megacaps%20sank%203.1%20per%20cent.%20A%20UBS%20basket%20of%20US%20stocks%20negatively%20impacted%20by%20tariffs%20sank%202.9%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEffects%20were%20also%20seen%20in%20Asian%20and%20Australian%20markets%2C%20with%20Tokyo%2C%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Sydney%20shares%20down.%C2%A0The%20benchmark%20Nikkei%20225%20index%20plunged%202.43%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20the%20broader%20Topix%20index%20lost%201.48%20per%20cent..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20shares%20also%20opened%20lower%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20tracking%20Asian%20peers.%C2%A0The%20Nifty%2050%20fell%200.64%20per%20cent%20to%2021%2C979.85%20by%209%3A15%20a.m.%20IST%2C%20while%20the%20BSE%20Sensex%20lost%200.45%20per%20cent%20to%2072%2C753.64.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2013%20major%20sectors%20logged%20losses%20at%20the%20open%2C%20while%20the%20broader%20small-%20and%20mid-caps%20fell%20about%201%20per%20cent%20each.%C2%A0The%20MSCI%20Asia%20ex-Japan%20dropped%20about%200.6%20per%20cent%2C%20tracking%20an%20overnight%20decline%20in%20Wall%20Street%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20wary%20about%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions%20and%20the%20prospect%20of%20tit-for-tat%20tariffs%20worsening%20the%20global%20trade%20spat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAutomaker%20shares%20fell%20sharply%2C%20with%20General%20Motors%2C%20which%20has%20significant%20truck%20production%20in%20Mexico%2C%20down%204%20per%20cent%20and%20Ford%20falling%201.7%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGustavo%20Flores-Macias%2C%20a%20public%20policy%20professor%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20said%20consumers%20could%20see%20price%20hikes%20within%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20automobile%20sector%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20see%20considerable%20negative%20consequences%2C%20not%20only%20because%20of%20the%20disruption%20of%20the%20supply%20chains%20that%20crisscross%20the%20three%20countries%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20process%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20the%20expected%20increase%20in%20the%20price%20of%20vehicles%2C%20which%20can%20dampen%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Flores-Macias%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Plan%20For%20Reciprocal%20Tariff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED