.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkims-sister-threatens-response-to-us-carriers-deployment-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F118697238.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkims-sister-threatens-response-to-us-carriers-deployment-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F118697238.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Cryptocurrencies%20Trump%20Wants%20US%20To%20Hold%20In%20Reserve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20named%20five%20cryptocurrencies%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20new%20strategic%20reserve%20-%20in%20other%20words%2C%20crypto%20holdings%20owned%20by%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Trump%20announced%20that%20his%20January%20executive%20order%20on%20digital%20assets%20would%20create%20a%20stockpile%20of%20XRP%2C%20SOL%20and%20ADA%20currencies%2C%20surprising%20traders%20by%20choosing%20three%20lesser-known%20tokens%20and%20sending%20their%20prices%20soaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Trump%20added%20that%20bitcoin%20and%20ether%2C%20the%20two%20biggest%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20would%20be%20included%20in%20the%20reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114093946326587357%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20what%20we%20know%20about%20the%20tokens%2C%20in%20the%20order%20Trump%20named%20them%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20XRP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreated%20by%20the%20US%20crypto%20company%20Ripple%2C%20XRP%20is%20the%20world's%20third-biggest%20cryptocurrency%2C%20with%20%24140%20billion%20of%20the%20tokens%20in%20circulation%2C%20and%20each%20token%20worth%20around%20%242.40%2C%20according%20to%20CoinGecko%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERipple%20has%20touted%20XRP%20as%20a%20way%20to%20help%20transfer%20funds%20around%20the%20world%20faster%20and%20more%20cheaply%20than%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20including%20bitcoin.%20Like%20other%20tokens%2C%20its%20price%20has%20been%20volatile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERipple%20is%20a%20major%20player%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20crypto%20lobbying.%20It%20donated%20%2445%20million%20to%20a%20lobbying%20group%20that%20tried%20to%20influence%20the%20US%20elections%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20crypto%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20OpenSecrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20its%20CEO%20Brad%20Garlinghouse%20posted%20a%20photo%20of%20himself%20alongside%20Trump%2C%20saying%20they%20had%20enjoyed%20a%20%26quot%3BGreat%20dinner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20company%20was%20locked%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20with%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20over%20whether%20its%20sales%20of%20XRP%20in%202012%20counted%20as%20an%20unregistered%20securities%20offering.%20Ripple%20mostly%20won%20that%20case%2C%20though%20the%20SEC%20did%20have%20a%20partial%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20for%20comment%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20Ripple%20spokesperson%20referred%20Reuters%20to%20a%20tweet%20Garlinghouse%20published%20on%20X%20on%20Sunday%20in%20which%20he%20said%20he%20appreciated%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bvision%20of%20a%20govt%20digital%20asset%20reserve%20representative%20of%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERipple's%20President%20Monica%20Long%20told%20Reuters%20in%20June%20that%20the%20PAC%20that%20Ripple%20had%20donated%20to%20was%20bipartisan%20and%20focused%20on%20supporting%20candidates%20who%20back%20the%20regulations%20desired%20by%20the%20crypto%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20SOL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESOL%20is%20the%20name%20of%20the%20token%20that%20runs%20on%20a%20blockchain%20called%20Solana.%20That%20blockchain%20is%20often%20used%20to%20launch%20meme%20coins%20-%20including%20Trump's%20own%20cryptocurrency%2C%20which%20the%20president%20unveiled%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20%2473%20billion%20worth%20of%20tokens%20in%20circulation%2C%20CoinGecko%20data%20puts%20it%20as%20the%20sixth-biggest%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20volatile%20and%20lost%20most%20of%20its%20value%20in%202022%2C%20hurt%20by%20its%20association%20with%20former%20FTX%20CEO%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried.%20Although%20Solana%20was%20not%20directly%20related%20to%20the%20now-collapsed%20crypto%20exchange%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20frequently%20praised%20the%20token.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20relatively%20newer%20player%20in%20crypto%2C%20Solana%20saw%20the%20price%20of%20its%20token%20soar%20in%202021%20when%20it%20was%20talked%20up%20as%20a%20rival%20to%20ether%20and%20because%20of%20its%20use%20in%20the%20then-booming%20market%20in%20non-fungible%20tokens%20(NFTs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolana's%20website%20says%20it%20is%20managed%20by%20%26quot%3BSolana%20Foundation%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20describes%20itself%20as%20a%20non-profit%20foundation%20based%20in%20Zug%20in%20Switzerland.%20Lily%20Liu%20and%20Daniel%20Albert%20are%20listed%20as%20the%20foundation's%20executive%20directors.%20Reuters%20was%20not%20able%20to%20immediately%20reach%20those%20connected%20with%20Solana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20ADA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EADA%20runs%20on%20a%20blockchain%20called%20Cardano.%20It%20was%20founded%20in%202015%20by%20Charles%20Hoskinson%2C%20a%20well-known%20US%20tech%20entrepreneur%20and%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20%2431.4%20billion%20worth%20of%20ADA%20tokens%20in%20circulation%2C%20according%20to%20CoinGecko%2C%20making%20it%20the%20eighth-biggest%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20token's%20price%20was%20the%20biggest%20gainer%20after%20Trump's%20announcement%2C%20briefly%20soaring%20more%20than%2070%25%20above%20its%20level%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECardano's%20website%20lists%20five%20entities%2C%20including%20a%20Switzerland-based%20non-profit%2C%20called%20the%20Cardano%20Foundation%2C%20and%20a%20for-profit%20arm%2C%20called%20Emurgo.%20Cardano%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Bitcoin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20and%20biggest%20cryptocurrency%2C%20bitcoin%20started%20circulating%20in%202009%2C%20created%20by%20a%20mysterious%20figure%20identified%20only%20as%20Satoshi%20Nakamoto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20other%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20primarily%20a%20way%20to%20move%20money%20between%20people%20without%20using%20intermediaries%20such%20as%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20individual%20bitcoin%20costs%20around%20%2486%2C000%20and%20there%20are%20around%20%241.7%20trillion%20worth%20of%20the%20tokens%20in%20circulation%2C%20CoinGecko%20data%20shows%2C%20meaning%20it%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20%243%20trillion%20in%20nominal%20value%20of%20all%20digital%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20surged%20last%20year%2C%20helped%20by%20the%20US%20SEC%20in%20January%202024%20allowing%20it%20to%20be%20included%20in%20exchange-traded%20funds%20and%20by%20Trump's%20election%20in%20November%2C%20which%20raised%20expectations%20for%20a%20wave%20of%20pro-crypto%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Ether%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEther%20is%20the%20cryptocurrency%20of%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20be%20a%20major%20player%20in%20decentralised%20finance%20(DeFi)%20-%20the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20use%20of%20blockchain%20technology%20to%20offer%20financial%20services%20without%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202013-2014%20by%20Vitalik%20Buterin%20and%20others%20to%20compete%20with%20bitcoin%2C%20its%20token%2C%20ether%2C%20trades%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20bitcoin's%20price%20but%20is%20still%20the%20second-biggest%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorld%20Liberty%20Financial%2C%20a%20crypto%20company%20Trump%20and%20his%20sons%20announced%20last%20year%2C%20has%20issued%20digital%20tokens%20on%20the%20Ethereum%20blockchain%20that%20it%20has%20so%20far%20sold%20for%20over%20%24500%20million.%20World%20Liberty%20said%20in%20February%20it%20was%20unveiling%20a%20strategic%20token%20reserve%20designed%20to%20bolster%20bitcoin%2C%20ethereum%20and%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20%26quot%3Bthat%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20reshaping%20global%20finance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ethereum%20Foundation%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741060140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9s1ge9a_cryptocurrency-istock_625x300_03_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-cryptocurrencies-donald-trump-wants-us-to-hold-in-reserve-7841885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22XRP%2C%20SOL%2C%20ADA%2C%20Bitcoin%20and%20Ether%20are%20the%20five%20cryptocurrencies%20named%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20reserve.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F5-cryptocurrencies-donald-trump-wants-us-to-hold-in-reserve-7841885%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Florida%20Congressman%20Lincoln%20D%C3%ADaz-Balart%20dies%20at%2070%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741059792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118697046%2Cimgsize-920558.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.c