2%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yogi%20Adityanath%20On%20Why%20Kumbh%20Stampede%20Was%20Not%20%26quot%3BExcessively%20Highlighted%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20on%20Monday%20said%20his%20government%20acted%20swiftly%20to%20control%20the%20situation%20after%20the%20January%2029%20stampede%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20medical%20aid%20for%20victims%20while%20preventing%20widespread%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20gathering%20of%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20(IIM)%20and%20Indian%20Postal%20Service%20officials%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20allow%20the%20incident%20to%20be%20excessively%20highlighted%20as%20eight%20crore%20devotees%20and%20sadhus%20were%20present%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20area%20at%20the%20time%20and%20panic%20could%20have%20worsened%20the%20situation.%26quot%3B%20At%20least%2030%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2060%20others%20injured%20in%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20Sangam%20ghat%20on%20Mauni%20Amavasya%2C%20a%20key%20bathing%20day%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20noted%20that%20apart%20from%20millions%20of%20devotees%2C%20seers%20and%20sadhus%20from%2013%20Akhadas%20were%20also%20scheduled%20to%20take%20the%20ritualistic%20'Amrit%20Snan'%20(holy%20dip)%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20two%20major%20challenges%20often%20arise%20in%20such%20events%20--%20determining%20the%20bathing%20order%20among%20the%20Akharas%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20led%20to%20disputes%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20ritual%20proceeds%20smoothly%20at%20the%20scheduled%20time%20of%204%20AM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20tragedy%2C%20all%20Akhadas%20were%20prepared%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20'snan'%2C%20but%20the%20administration%20intervened%20to%20postpone%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20requested%20them%20to%20delay%20the%20ritual%20to%20manage%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20officials%20closely%20monitored%20the%20crowd%2C%20evacuated%20the%20Sangam%20area%20by%20noon%2C%20and%20ensured%20the%20'snan'%20resumed%20by%202%3A30%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20effective%20crisis%20management%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20difficult%20situations%2C%20many%20people%20panic%20and%20give%20up%2C%20but%20we%20must%20develop%20the%20strength%20to%20make%20firm%20decisions%20with%20patience%20and%20control.%26quot%3B%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20effective%20coordination%20among%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20devotees%2C%20sadhus%20and%20administrative%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20initiated%20dialogues%20to%20maintain%20order%20and%20ensure%20smooth%20execution%20of%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20faced%20with%20adversity%2C%20many%20people%20give%20up%2C%20assuming%20that%20things%20will%20take%20their%20course.%20However%2C%20true%20leadership%20lies%20in%20tackling%20challenges%20with%20composure%2C%20just%20as%20we%20did%20during%20Maha%20Kumbh%20to%20ensure%20its%20smooth%20execution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20held%20once%20every%2012%20years%2C%20attracts%20millions%20of%20pilgrims%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20making%20crowd%20management%20a%20critical%20challenge%20for%20authorities.%20This%20year%2C%20over%2066%20crore%20pilgrims%20attended%20the%20religious%20event%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20which%20has%20been%20projecting%20it%20as%20a%20major%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20also%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20patience%20and%20resilience%20in%20handling%20difficult%20situations%2C%20citing%20the%20successful%20execution%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20programme%20on%20%26quot%3BNation-Building%20through%20the%20Successful%20Organization%20of%20Mahakumbh%2C%26quot%3B%20held%20with%20officials%20from%20IIM%20and%20the%20Indian%20Postal%20Service%2C%20he%20highlighted%20how%20effective%20crisis%20management%20ensured%20a%20smooth%20and%20orderly%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20noted%20that%20Mahakumbh%20teaches%20patience%20and%20adherence%20to%20natural%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20past%20reports%20by%20international%20media%20and%20UNESCO%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20pointed%20out%20that%20earlier%20editions%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20were%20often%20associated%20with%20chaos%2C%20mismanagement%2C%20and%20filth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202019%2C%20we%20aimed%20to%20change%20that%20perception.%20When%20we%20step%20away%20from%20the%20beaten%20path%20and%20do%20something%20different%2C%20it%20becomes%20memorable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20incident%20from%20the%202013%20Kumbh%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Yogi%2C%20I%20was%20at%20my%20camp%20in%20Prayagraj%20when%20I%20read%20news%20reports%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Mauritius%20had%20visited%20but%20refused%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20due%20to%20pollution.%20He%20merely%20offered%20his%20prayers%20from%20a%20distance%20and%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20incident%20stayed%20with%20me.%20A%20foreign%20dignitary%20came%20to%20our%20sacred%20event%20and%20left%20disappointed.%20It%20meant%20there%20was%20a%20flaw%20in%20our%20preparations%2C%20and%20we%20needed%20to%20fix%20it.%26quot%3B%20Underlining%20the%202019%20Kumbh's%20emphasis%20on%20hygiene%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20explained%20that%20the%20event%20site%2C%20located%20on%20sandy%20riverbanks%2C%20previously%20had%20unsanitary%20toilet%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanitation%20facilities%20were%20makeshift%2C%20leading%20to%20unbearable%20stench%2C%20flies%2C%20mosquitoes%2C%20and%20potential%20disease%20outbreaks.%20We%20changed%20this%20by%20installing%20one%20lakh%20properly%20managed%20toilets%20with%20routine%20cleaning%2C%20ensuring%20not%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20sewage%20entered%20the%20Ganga%20or%20Yamuna%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20credited%20the%20police%20for%20their%20role%20in%20maintaining%20security%20and%20managing%20crowds%20efficiently.%20%26quot%3BFor%20any%20large-scale%20event%2C%20crowd%20management%20is%20critical.%20A%20sense%20of%20safety%20among%20attendees%20is%20paramount.%20In%202019%2C%20we%20introduced%20special%20four-month%20training%20programs%20for%20police%20personnel%20to%20enhance%20their%20preparedness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20the%202025%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20turnout%20exceeded%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20estimated%20that%20the%20crowd%20would%20double%20compared%20to%202019%2C%20but%20the%20actual%20numbers%20surpassed%20all%20records.%20This%20required%20significant%20expansion%20in%20event%20planning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparations%20for%202025%20included%20expanding%20the%20fairgrounds%2C%20increasing%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20designating%20parking%20and%20holding%20areas%20across%20neighbouring%20districts%20like%20Mirzapur%2C%20Bhadohi%2C%20Kaushambi%2C%20Jaunpur%2C%20Fatehpur%2C%20Pratapgarh%2C%20Chitrakoot%2C%20and%20Rae%20Bareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20railway%20station%20claimed%2042%20lives.%20Learning%20from%20that%2C%20we%20expanded%20not%20just%20the%20main%20Prayagraj%20Junction%20but%20nine%20other%20railway%20stations%20and%20the%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20stressed%20that%20religious%20gatherings%20are%20inherently%20disciplined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%202025%20Mahakumbh%2C%20a%20minor%20stampede%20occurred%20between%201%3A15%20AM%20and%201%3A30%20AM%20on%20January%2028-29%2C%20while%20over%20four%20crore%20people%20were%20present%20at%20the%20venue.%20Yet%2C%20within%2015%20minutes%2C%20people%20voluntarily%20created%20a%20green%20corridor%2C%20allowing%20medical%20teams%20to%20reach%20the%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20highlighted%20the%20economic%20benefits%20of%20such%20large-scale%20religious%20events.%20%26quot%3BMaha%20Kumbh%20contributes%20significantly%20to%20the%20economy.%20It%20provides%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20supports%20various%20businesses.%20Previously%20overlooked%2C%20its%20economic%20impact%20is%20now%20being%20recognised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaha%20Kumbh%202025%20was%20held%20from%20January%2013%20(Paush%20Purnima)%20to%20February%2026%20(Maha%20Shivaratri)%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20time%20the%20fair%20lasted%20until%20Maha%20Shivaratri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20past%20editions%2C%20the%20event%20would%20wind%20down%20after%20Basant%20Panchami%2C%20leaving%20only%20Kalpvasis.%20This%20time%2C%20daily%20attendance%20after%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20ranged%20from%201.5%20to%201.75%20crore%20people.%20On%20Basant%20Panchami%2C%20around%20three%20crore%20people%20participated%2C%20while%20on%20Magh%20Purnima%2C%20the%20count%20was%20two%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20international%20participation%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20event%20saw%20visits%20of%20the%20President%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20governors%2C%20chief%20ministers%2C%2074%20ambassadors%20and%20high%20commissioners%2C%20Bhutan's%20King%2C%2012%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20and%20representatives%20from%20over%20100%20countries.%20Business%20leaders%2C%20film%20stars%2C%20and%20cricketers%20also%20took%20part.%26quot%3B%20The%20CM%20mentioned%20UNESCO's%20interest%20in%20studying%20Mahakumbh's%20environmental%20impact.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ensured%20that%20no%20sewage%20or%20industrial%20waste%20entered%20the%20Ganga.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%20Kanpur%2C%20four%20crore%20litres%20of%20sewage%20used%20to%20flow%20into%20the%20river%20daily.%20We%20had%20it%20sealed%20off%20three%20years%20ago.%20Today%2C%20not%20a%20single%20drop%20enters%20the%20Ganga%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20highlighted%20Maha%20Kumbh's%20role%20in%20national%20unity%2C%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20and%20environmental%20conservation%2C%20aligning%20with%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20%26quot%3BEk%20Bharat%2C%20Shreshtha%20Bharat.%26quot%3B%20He%20emphasised%20that%20the%20event%20transcended%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20language%20barriers%2C%20bringing%20millions%20together%20in%20devotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20invested%20Rs%207%2C500%20crore%2C%20with%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%20allocated%20for%20infrastructure%20in%20Prayagraj%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%20%26quot%3BThis%20ensured%20better%20connectivity%2C%20sanitation%2C%20and%20essential%20facilities%20for%20pilgrims%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECultural%20and%20religious%20landmarks%20were%20also%20developed%2C%20including%2012%20corridors%20linked%20to%20Akshayavat%2C%20Saraswati%20Koop%2C%20and%20Maharishi%20Bharadwaj.%20%26quot%3BThese%20sites%20now%20reflect%20our%20heritage%20and%20spiritual%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMaha%20Kumbh%20teaches%20patience%20and%20discipline.%20Whether%20for%20faith%20or%20economy%2C%20such%20events%20leave%20a%20lasting%20impact%20and%20contribute%20to%20national%20development.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%2