%3E%20in%202016%20in%20a%20rare%20public%20statement%20for%20the%20couple's%2050th%20wedding%20anniversary.%20%26quot%3BMy%20second%20thought%20was%2C%20'Lord%20she's%20good%20lookin.'%26quot%3B%20And%20that%20was%20the%20day%20my%20life%20began.%20I%20wouldn't%20trade%20the%20last%2050%20years%20for%20nothing%20on%20this%20earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%20of%20dating%2C%20they%20married%20in%201966%20in%20a%20private%20ceremony%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20marriage%2C%20Dean%20has%20largely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdolly-parton-carl-thomas-dean-husband-red-carpet-events-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estayed%20out%20of%20the%20spotlight%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParton%20received%20her%20first%20songwriting%20award%20in%201966%20for%20%26quot%3BPut%20It%20Off%20Until%20Tomorrow%26quot%3B%20recorded%20by%20Bill%20Phillips.%20Parton%20and%20Dean%20attended%20the%20ceremony%20and%20dinner%20together%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20continue%20making%20joint%20public%20appearances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20dinner%2C%20we%20walked%20back%20out%2C%20and%20they%20brought%20us%20our%20car%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20even%20remember%20what%20we%20were%20driving%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20got%20in%20it%20and%20headed%20for%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Parton%20said%20at%20the%20Marty%20Stuart%20Jam%20in%202011%2C%20per%20country%20music%20news%20site%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheboot.com%2Fdolly-parton-husband-carl-dean%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Boot%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BCarl%20turned%20to%20me%20and%20said%2C%20'Dolly%2C%20I%20want%20you%20to%20have%20everything%20you%20want%2C%20and%20I'm%20happy%20for%20you%2C%20but%20don't%20you%20ever%20ask%20me%20to%20go%20to%20another%20one%20of%20them%20dang%20things%20again!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean%20also%20inspired%20one%20of%20Parton's%20biggest%20hits%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdolly-parton-interesting-things-you-didnt-know%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJolene%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20for%20the%20song%20came%20from%20a%20bank%20teller%20who%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20crush%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20husband%2C%20Parton%20said%20in%20a%202008%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2008%2F10%2F09%2F95520570%2Fdolly-partons-jolene-still-haunts-singers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20just%20loved%20going%20to%20the%20bank%20because%20she%20paid%20him%20so%20much%20attention.%20It%20was%20kinda%20like%20a%20running%20joke%20between%20us%20%E2%80%94%20when%20I%20was%20saying%2C%20'Hell%2C%20you're%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20the%20bank.%20I%20don't%20believe%20we've%20got%20that%20kind%20of%20money.'%20So%20it's%20really%20an%20innocent%20song%20all%20around%2C%20but%20sounds%20like%20a%20dreadful%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20singer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdolly-parton-husband-carl-dean-typical-date-night-homecooked-dinner-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypical%20date%20night%20with%20her%20husband%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20a%20romantic%20dinner%20at%20home%2C%20during%20which%20they%20would%20both%20get%20dressed%20up%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20been%20sweethearts%20as%20well%20as%20being%20best%20friends%2C%20as%20well%20as%20being%20husband%20and%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20just%20decide%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Parton%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20singer%20had%20no%20additional%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdolly-parton-husban