s%20with%20just%20a%20few%20taps.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.404media.co%2Finstagram-ads-send-this-nudify-site-90-percent-of-its-traffic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E404%20Media%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20Instagram%20has%20struggled%20to%20take%20down%20ads%20for%20these%20kinds%20of%20apps%2C%20which%20are%20against%20Meta's%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Thorn%2C%20an%20organization%20that%20advocates%20against%20online%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20and%20exploitation%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thorn.org%2Fresearch%2Flibrary%2Fdeepfake-nudes-and-young-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20a%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20its%20survey%20of%2013-to-20-year-olds%3A%20It%20said%20one%20out%20of%20eight%20young%20people%20who%20responded%20said%20they%C2%A0knew%20someone%20personally%20who%20had%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20a%20deepfake%20nude%20image.%20These%20images%2C%20sickeningly%2C%20put%20a%20victim's%20real%20face%20on%20an%20AI-generated%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20closing%20a%20key%20legal%20gap%2C%20this%20bill%20criminalizes%20the%20knowing%20distribution%20of%20intimate%20visual%20depictions%20of%20minors%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20real%20or%20AI-generated%20%E2%80%94%20when%20shared%20with%20intent%20to%20harm%2C%20harass%2C%20or%20exploit%2C%26quot%3B%20Emily%20Slifer%2C%20Thorn's%20director%20of%20policy%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20people%20affected%2C%20such%20images%20can%20be%20devastating.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F08%2Ftechnology%2Fdeepfake-ai-nudes-westfield-high-school.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20called%20the%20issue%20an%20%26quot%3Bepidemic%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20story%20about%20how%20AI%20images%20have%20wreaked%20havoc%20in%20suburban%20high%20schools%20and%20middle%20schools.%20During%20Monday's%20roundtable%2C%20several%20you