g-form-viewing-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20TV%20viewership%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20starting%20to%20boost%20ad%20revenue%20for%20some%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Matter%2C%20who%20has%2028%20million%20subscribers%2C%20makes%20challenge%20and%20skit-based%20videos%20featuring%20his%20daughter.%20In%20the%20past%2028%20days%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%2065%25%20of%20his%20channel's%20total%20ad%20revenue%20came%20from%20TV%2C%20despite%20TV%20viewers%20accounting%20for%2045%25%20of%20his%20total%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20YouTube%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-do-youtubers-make%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreator%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20TV%20were%20up%20by%20more%20than%2030%25%20year%20over%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20including%20Matter%20are%20developing%20longer%20videos%20and%20compilations%20as%20they%20chase%20TV%20viewers%20and%20ad%20dollars.%20Longer%20videos%20can%20include%20more%20ad%20breaks%2C%20thus%20boosting%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%2045-minute%20video%2C%20you%20can%20have%20three%20or%20four%20different%20ad-break%20segments%2C%26quot%3B%3Csub%3E%20%3C%2Fsub%3EDan%20Weinstein%2C%20a%20cofounder%20and%20co-CEO%20of%20Underscore%20Talent%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeinstein%20said%20that%20combining%20existing%20videos%20in%20compilations%20was%20also%20an%20easy%20way%20for%20short-form%20content%20creators%20to%20join%20the%20TV%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20funny%2C%20viral%20short-form%20stuff%20actually%20does%20tend%20to%20do%20pretty%20well%20if%20sort%20of%20strung%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Weinstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22158ecf4c-55b0-4235-b143-6132d9240a47%5C%22%3EMaking%20extra-long%20videos%20by%20piecing%20together%20shorter%20ones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYouTubers%20don't%20need%20highly%20produced%20Netflix-style%20shows%20to%20do%20well%20on%20TV.%20Victor%20Potrel%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20partnerships%20and%20creator%20services%20at%20the%20digital-media%20company%20TheSoul%20Publishing%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20YouTube%20consumption%20on%20the%20TV%20as%20an%20accelerating%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20the%20evolution%20of%20people%20gradually%20changing%20their%20consuming%20habits%20but%20wanting%20the%20same%20content%20on%20their%20TV%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20Potrel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheSoul%20manages%20several%20YouTube%20channels%2C%20including%205-Minute%20Crafts%2C%20Bright%20Side%2C%20and%20123%20Go.%20For%20TV%2C%20Potrel%20said%2C%20TheSoul%20packages%20videos%20based%20on%20themes%20such%20as%20home%20decor%20and%20builds%20them%20into%20hourslong%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20radically%20change%20the%20way%20that%20you%20produce%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20Potrel%20said.%20%26quot%3BMostly%20it's%20been%20about%20packaging%20the%20content%20and%20adapting%20it%20for%20the%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20TheSoul's%20share%20of%20global%20views%20on%20connected%20TVs%20rose%20to%2024%25%20in%202024%20from%2017%25%20in%202022%2C%20and%20watch%20time%20increased%20to%2041%25%20from%2028%25.%20Global%20emerging%20markets%20have%20also%20shown%20an%20increase%20in%20TV%20viewership%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0for%20instance%2C%20views%20of%20TheSoul's%20content%20on%20connected%20TVs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20India%20doubled%20from%202022%20to%202024%2C%20reaching%2010%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERevenue%20has%20increased%20as%20well.%20Potrel%20said%20longer%20watch%20times%20had%20led%20to%20higher%20ad%20rates%20for%20TheSoul's%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffe964a7-c8e2-4baa-9701-4f744e43eaf2%5C%22%3EReaching%20different%20audiences%20on%20TVs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYouTubers%20are%20trying%20to%20appeal%20to%20both%20kids%20and%20Gen%20Z%20viewers%20on%20TV.%20Their%20viewing%20behaviors%20are%20very%20different%20%E2%80%94%20kids%20may%20sit%20down%20to%20watch%20more%20engaging%20pieces%20of%20content%2C%20while%20Gen%20Zers%20may%20listen%20to%20videos%20in%20the%20background%20while%20multitasking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Matter%2C%20who%20makes%20videos%20for%20kids%2C%20his%20team%20has%20adapted%20in%20two%20ways%3A%20They've%20doubled%20the%20length%20of%20the%20videos%20and%20elevated%20production%20quality%20with%20subtitles%20and%20video%20graphics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiana%20Parker%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20programming%20and%20content%20at%20the%20sketch-comedy%20YouTube%20channel%20Smosh%2C%20said%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20viewers%20tended%20to%20enjoy%20accessible%20content%20on%20TV%20that%20doesn't%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20background%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20you%20put%20on%20and%20be%20busy%20folding%20your%20laundry%20to%2C%20or%20go%20run%20out%20of%20the%20room%20to%20grab%20something%20and%20come%20back%20and%20still%20feel%20like%20you%20didn't%20miss%20the%20entire%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Parker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20most%20of%20Smosh's%20content%20is%2030%20to%2045%20minutes%20long%2C%20comparable%20to%20a%20TV%20series.%20The%20Smosh%20Pit%20YouTube%20channel%20used%20to%20frequently%20upload%2012-%20to%2015-minute%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20current%20production%20value%20splits%20the%20difference%20between%20quality%20but%20also%20casualness%2C%26quot%3B%20Parker%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20editing%20style%20is%20more%20free-form%2C%20where%20the%20editors%20are%20inserting%20jokes%20into%20the%20video%20or%20we%20leave%20in%20a%20blooper.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Smosh%20team%20is%20continuing%20to%20explore%20new%20strategies%20and%20create%20content%20for%20larger%20screens%20%E2%80%94%20partly%20because%20it's%20reading%20the%20tea%20leaves%20on%20where%20YouTube%20is%20headed%20as%20a%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20YouTube%20is%20reall