discovery%20of%20three%20rock%20shelters.%20One%20of%20these%20contained%20stunning%20prehistoric%20paintings%20depicting%20animals%2C%20geometric%20patterns%2C%20and%20human%20figures%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paintings%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Megalithic%20(Iron%20Age)%20and%20early%20historic%20periods%20(2500%20BCE-2nd%20century%20CE)%2C%20were%20created%20using%20natural%20materials%20like%20red%20ochre%2C%20kaolin%2C%20animal%20fat%2C%20and%20crushed%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rock%20inscriptions%2C%20dating%20between%204th%20and%2016th%20Century%20CE%2C%20suggest%20that%20Lankamala%20was%20a%20major%20Shaivite%20pilgrim%20center%20regularly%20visited%20by%20devotees%20from%20north%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4m50cvi8_andhra-asi-findings-2_625x300_03_March_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20in%20the%20rugged%20terrain%20of%20Nityapujakona%2C%20Akkadevatala%20Konda%20and%20Bandigani%20Chella%20%C2%A0located%20South%20of%20Srisailam%2C%20took%20place%20between%20February%2027%20and%20March%201%2C%20and%20looked%20into%20nearly%2030%20inscriptions%20in%20the%20reserve%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scripts%20of%20the%20inscriptions%20were%20Brahmi%20(4th%20Century%20CE)%2C%20Shell%20(6th%20Century%20CE)%2C%20Nagari%20(Sanskrit)%20and%20Telugu%20characters%20among%20the%20inscriptions%2C%20said%20K%20Munirathnam%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20landmark%20discovery%20in%20the%20ASI's%20history.%20It%20helps%20us%20ascertain%20the%20pilgrimage%20routes%20which%20even%20North%20Indians%20took.%20It%20shows%20how%20the%20pilgrimage%20centre%20of%20the%20Shaivite%20region%20shifted%20from%20here%20to%20Srisailam%20starting%20in%20the%204th%20Century%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20discoveries%2C%20he%20said%20the%20local%20Forest%20Range%20Officer%20sent%20them%20pictures%2C%20after%20which%20the%20ASI%20wrote%20to%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Pawan%20Kalyan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20then%20embarked%20on%20an%20arduous%20trek%20going%20up%20thousands%20of%20feet%20on%20steep%20hills%20to%20copy%20the%20inscriptions%20through%20the%20dangerous%20forests%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Munirathnam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchaeologists%20said%20the%20texts%20provide%20valuable%20insights%20into%20the%20region's%20past%2C%20shedding%20light%20on%20its%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741023660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ftrf8p8t8_andhra-asi-findings-_625x300_03_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeep-in-andhra-forest-treasure-trove-of-rock-paintings-inscriptions-7840448%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20inscriptions%20--%20800%20to%202000%20years%20old%20-%20have%20been%20discovered%20at%20Kadapa's%20Lankkamala%20Reserve%20Forest%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20survey%20by%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20also%20found%20rock%20art%20thought%20to%20be%20from%20the%20megalithic%20period.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeep-in-andhra-forest-treasure-trove-of-rock-paintings-inscriptions-7840448%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'America%20will%20not%20put%20up%20with%20this!'%3A%20Trump%20hits%20out%20at%20Zelenskyy%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741022760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-donald-trump-volodymyr-zelenskyy_6842610.jpg%3F20250228200611